msgstr "Wyślij certyfikat na mój adres e-mail"

msgid "plugins.generic.reviewerCertificate.myCertificates.emailSent"
msgstr "Certyfikat został wysłany na Twój adres e-mail."

msgid "plugins.generic.reviewerCertificate.myCertificates.emailError"
msgstr "Nie udało się wysłać wiadomości. Spróbuj ponownie później lub skontaktuj się z redakcją czasopisma."

msgid "plugins.generic.reviewerCertificate.settings.ackEmailSubject"
msgstr "Temat wiadomości z podziękowaniem"

msgid "plugins.generic.reviewerCertificate.settings.ackEmailBody"
msgstr "Treść wiadomości z podziękowaniem"

msgid "plugins.generic.reviewerCertificate.settings.ackEmailDescription"
msgstr "List wysyłany do recenzenta ze strony „Moje certyfikaty\" z załączonym certyfikatem PDF. Obsługuje te same zmienne szablonu co treść certyfikatu oraz {{$editorName}}."

msgid "plugins.generic.reviewerCertificate.emailCertificate.attachmentFallback"
msgstr "Nie udało się załączyć pliku PDF certyfikatu do tej wiadomości (może przekraczać limit rozmiaru serwera pocztowego). Certyfikat można pobrać tutaj:"

msgid "plugins.generic.reviewerCertificate.emailCertificate.defaultSubject"
msgstr "Acknowledgement of your review for {{$journalName}}"

msgid "plugins.generic.reviewerCertificate.emailCertificate.defaultBody"
msgstr "Dear {{$reviewerName}},\n\nWe are immensely grateful for your efforts and time devoted to reviewing the manuscript entitled \"{{$submissionTitle}}\" submitted to {{$journalName}}. Your meticulous and insightful evaluation has provided valuable feedback that has helped the authors improve their work and advance their research endeavors.\n\nYour contribution to maintaining the quality of the articles published in our journal is highly appreciated. We understand that reviewing manuscripts is a demanding task, and we acknowledge the effort you put into thoroughly analyzing the submission and providing constructive criticism to the authors.\n\nTo show our appreciation for your hard work, we would like to kindly ask you to forward this letter to reviews@webofscience.com. Please note that in accordance with our editorial policy, the content of the review will remain confidential and will not be displayed on Web of Science.\n\nYour reviewer certificate is attached to this letter.\n\nOnce again, we extend our gratitude for your commitment to the advancement of research in your field. We hope to continue collaborating with you in the future.\n\nBest regards,\n\n{{$editorName}}\n{{$journalName}}"

